<P>
   &UR; The future is here in the technology of getting around. Today's
planes, trains and automobiles are your boarding pass, ticket and
license to the transportation of the future. &LR;   &UR; In a special
package, the Boston Globe offers a look at how technology is
striving to make our journeys faster, more comfortable and lots of
fun. &LR;
</P>
