   FINANCIAL-BUSINESS NEWS (``f'' category)
</P>
<P>
   HEARST-GEOCAST (New York) _ Hearst-Argyle Television, Inc. and
Geocast Network Systems, Inc., announce that they plan to deliver
over-the-air digital broadcasting to desktop PCs. By the Hearst
Newspapers.
</P>
<P>
   APPLE-LAPTOP (San Francisco) _ ``Can I touch it?'' Not the usual
sort of reaction you get when carrying around a laptop computer,
but that's pretty much the response I got when I strolled around
with the iBook, Apple Computer's new, stylish laptop that is being
shipped this month to computer stores. By MATT BEER.
</P>
