</P>
<P>
   FILM-HAPPY-PROFILE (Toronto) _ A movie about a little Texas town
could be one of the sleeper comedy hits of the year. The movie
``Happy, Texas'' embraces the state and its small towns. The movie
opens Friday. By LOUIS B. PARKS.
</P>
<P>
   VIDEO-REVIEW (Undated) _ Reviews of ``Young Frankenstein's'' 25
1/2 anniversary reissue, which includes 22 minutes of new footage,
with interview with actress Teri Garr. By BRUCE WESTBROOK.
</P>
<P>
   MUSIC-JAMES-BROWN (Undated) _ Godfather of Soul James Brown is
still alive and kickin' and speaking his mind about today's music
scene, education and his pre-celeb days as a janitor. By JOEY
GUERRA.
