Francisco's starting quarterback for Sunday's game against
undefeated St. Louis as ``double top secret.'' But Jeff Garcia will
in all likelihood get his second start for the team while Steve
Young gives his head a second week of rest from its Sept. 27
concussion. By JOHN CRUMPACKER.
</P>
<P>
   COMMENTARY (``k'' category) _ As one of America's most
vociferous and relentless critics of cellular phones, I must make a
confession: Last month, during a three-week working vacation in
Italy, I used a cell phone and it felt really, really good. Worse,
I used it during a meal in a restaurant, an act for which I once
suggested prison time. By STEPANIE SALTER.
</P>
