<HEADLINE>
KANSAS CITY STAR BUDGET 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
   
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Kansas City Star plans to move the following stories for use
by clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs and PMs of Friday,
Oct. 8. If you have any questions, please call The Star's News Desk
at (816) 234-4720.
</P>
<P>
   GUNS: Federal and local authorities are about to start a new
