<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    POST-BHOPAL REFORMS PREPARE U.S. FOR Y2K
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By MARILYN GEEWAX
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
