<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CLINTON-SENATE-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
HILLARY CLINTON COMPLETES LEGAL REQUIREMENT FOR N.Y. CANDIDACY 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDS: Filed in ``w'' and ``p'' categories)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By STEWART M. POWELL  
 c.1999 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
