<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-07 18:04 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9794 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u k BC-MEANS-COLUMN-HNS &LR;      10-07 0843
