<SLUG> BC-CDC-FLU-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Elderly often pass on yearly flu shot
 &HT;    By Lillian Lee Kim
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ Many elderly people who don't get an annual flu shot
say they didn't know they needed one, or thought the vaccine could
give them the flu.
</P>
<P>
   Influenza kills 20,000 Americans every year _ and 90 percent of
