<SLUG> BC-SYPHILIS-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Syphilis down nationwide
 &HT;    By M.A.J. McKenna
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
