<P>
   CIRCUS-BAN (Seattle) _ Seattle may become the first big city in
the nation to ban performing circus animals. ``There are plenty of
circuses that don't depend on exotic animals doing tricks,'' says
Mayor Paul Schell. ``I think it's a form of entertainment that we
can live without in Seattle.''
</P>
<P>
   By Kristin Dizon. (Story will move in the ``a'' category.)
