Health, during a news conference announcing his appointment as
president of Memorial Sloan Kettering Hospital on Thursday. Varmus,
a Nobel-Prize winning molecular biologist, is widely regarded as an
effective administrator and will lead one of the nation's top
facilities on cancer research and treatment. (James Estrin/New York
Times Photo)
