<P>
   BC-ASTRODOME-FAREWELL-NYT (moved on Saturday, Oct. 2)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Saturday, Oct. 2,
about the end of baseball at the Houston Astrodome misstated the
affiliation of Stephen Klineberg, a sociologist who commented on
the structure's role in the city's history. He teaches at Rice
University, not the University of Houston.
</P>
</TEXT>
