<DOCNO> NYT19991007.0429 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-07 22:50 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0183 &Cx1f; taf-z
u p BC-NY-CLINTON-ART-NYT &LR;      10-07 0882
